Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(300,240,240,240,0,20000)\an5\an5\fs32\bord0.8\be5\fn方正宋三_GBK\4a&H64\3c&HFFFFFF&}中午12点32分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(240,240,0,240,0,160)\an5\an5\fs32\bord0.8\be5\fn方正宋三_GBK\4a&H64\3c&HFFFFFF&}中午12点32分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(720,274,300,274,0,160)\an5\fs32\bord0.8\be5\fn方正宋三_GBK\fad(160,0)\4a&H64\3c&HFFFFFF&}三河·武藏专用陆上港口
